CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 4, 1960, pg. A8 reads:"YMCA Marks 50th Anniversary - Centre Avenue YMCA celebrated its 50th anniversary on May 29 with a program at Warren Methodist Church. Above, left to right; B.H. Logan, chairman, Christian education committee; the Rev. William J. Harvey III, pastor, Macedonia Baptist Church; Atty. Byrd Brown, chairman, committee of management; Bishop Joseph Gomez, principal speaker; the Rev. Ramsey Bridges, member of committee and host pastor, and James M. Burgett, executive secretary, Centre Avenue YMCA. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: B. H. Logan, Rev. William J. Harvey III, Atty. Byrd Brown, Bishop Joseph Gomez, Rev. Ramsey Bridges, and James M. Burgett, standing in Warren Methodist Church for Centre Avenue YMCA fiftieth anniversary
